{"tid":1211210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"近排學校搞咗個壁報比賽","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T15:19:07.000Z","uid":98290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"90191394235c3864a226299345d575ca4c49d473","tid":1211210,"uid":98290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"近排學校搞左個壁報比賽<br />\n<br />\n作為班會會計, 諗咗啲物資要買, 想問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 索帶 (想整3D 壁報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n2. 較剪/ cutter (整壁報是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n3. 水同食物  (做做下餓餓地可以休息下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n4. 壁報紙/ 紙皮 (有時有啲同學太深近視都睇得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n5. 眼罩+口罩<br />\n6. 長遮+雨嬲<br />\n7. 頭盔<br />\n8. 鹽水<br />\n9. 保鮮紙<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇補充?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋呢啲物資係唔係擺近啲個壁報板會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057d53fdc2f79bf53f6e04f5a8af3d38613aed10","tid":1211210,"uid":98290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"個比賽好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫手諗下仲有冇野要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}